{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always remembered the [BACKGROUND NOISE] last words of my mother's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we said goodbye, she didn't tell me, I hope you survive, I hope you succeed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She told me two things, and this remained my testament. 'Remember who you are, and tell them that there was nobody to talk to.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I try to remember who I am.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I tried to behave in the way which would be proud of me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But it was-- when I look back, I understand much more than I understood then, because you can see the pattern.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can see how it evolved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can see what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It happened because they were very, very clever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They did it in a very perfidious, in a very methodical, in a very gradual way, and they did it in secrecy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One of the things, they did it because it was conducive-- the environment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody cared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody bothered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember when I was in Crossen an der Oder making some beds-- and this is when my Zionism started.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't-- I wasn't political, I told you before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I felt, of course they can do with us what they want.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They can treat us like vermin, because we have got nobody protect us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If we had a place to our own, somebody somewhere would be a voice who would say, look what is happening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In my simple way, this is how-- this was the awakening, because I realized we were treated like vermin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Nobody cared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Nobody voiced a protest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Nobody-- there was no contact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And now I read the history of that period, I even feel worse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But this is-- it is-- this is what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
